{"kind":"article","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Discover techniques for streaming high-quality audio to bandwidth-limited networks and new audio codec support. We’ll share some best practices for supporting the xHE-AAC, FLAC, and Apple Lossless Audio audio codecs, including limited support for multichannel AAC.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"anchor":"Related-Sessions","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Related Sessions"},{"type":"links","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10225-Improve-stream-authoring-with-HLS-Tools","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10230-Optimize-live-streams-with-HLS-Playlist-Delta-Updates","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10636-Whats-new-in-streaming-audio-for-Apple-Watch"],"style":"list"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"Deliver a better HLS audio experience","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC20","role":"sampleCode"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10158","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (19 min)"}},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10158-deliver-a-better-hls-audio-experience"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10158-Deliver-a-better-HLS-audio-experience","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"WWDC Notes","images":[{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","type":"icon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community.","type":"text"}]},"WWDC20-Icon.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","title":"Learn More…"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20":{"role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","title":"WWDC20","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 12, Swift 5.3, iOS 14, macOS 11 (Big Sur), tvOS 14, watchOS 7."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WidgetKit"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"StoreKit Testing"},{"type":"text","text":", and more."}]},"WWDC20.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20.jpeg"}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","alt":null},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10158":{"type":"download","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10158","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10158"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10225-Improve-stream-authoring-with-HLS-Tools":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10225-improve-stream-authoring-with-hls-tools","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10225-Improve-stream-authoring-with-HLS-Tools","role":"sampleCode","title":"Improve stream authoring with HLS Tools","abstract":[{"text":"Deliver live and on-demand audio and video to iPhone, iPad, Apple Watch, Mac, PC, and Apple TV with HTTP Live Streaming (HLS). Learn about tools and features to help improve the authoring of your HLS streams and provide low-latency delivery and better audio performance to people watching or listening to your content. We’ll also walk you through creating Low-Latency HLS test streams, integrating audio codecs, and creating master playlists.","type":"text"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10230-Optimize-live-streams-with-HLS-Playlist-Delta-Updates":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10230-Optimize-live-streams-with-HLS-Playlist-Delta-Updates","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover Playlist Delta Updates, an HLS feature that optimizes the delivery of live streams with large playback windows and lots of metadata. We’ll show you how Playlist Delta Updates can reduce overheard when producing live streams, provide higher-quality variants for people with slower connections, and integrate advertising."}],"type":"topic","title":"Optimize live streams with HLS Playlist Delta Updates","role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10230-optimize-live-streams-with-hls-playlist-delta-updates","kind":"article"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10636-Whats-new-in-streaming-audio-for-Apple-Watch":{"title":"What’s new in streaming audio for Apple Watch","kind":"article","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deliver a smooth streaming audio experience straight to the wrist. We’ll talk about some of the new things for building great streaming apps unique to Apple Watch. Learn how to integrate more audio formats, deliver streams more efficiently through new codecs, and add encrypted content to expand your app’s media library."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10636-Whats-new-in-streaming-audio-for-Apple-Watch","role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10636-whats-new-in-streaming-audio-for-apple-watch"}}}